# 4) Product operating model after re-architecture

## One brain, multiple surfaces

Backfill will operate as one shared action system with different channel-specific permissions and ergonomics.

### Voice

Best for:

* employee callouts
* quick manager status questions
* urgent simple approvals
* escalation requests

### SMS

Best for:

* short operational schedule changes
* publish/approve actions
* simple shift creation/editing
* status queries
* open shift actions

### Web AI prompt

Best for:

* complex schedule creation or edits
* bulk changes
* conflict resolution
* previewing diffs
* managerial planning requests

### Structured web UI

Best for:

* manual fallback
* deep review
* visual schedule manipulation
* roster maintenance
* settings and rules configuration

## Important strategic rule

The phone number becomes the **operational remote control**, not the entire admin cockpit.

The web app remains the **full workspace**, now with an AI prompt layer built into it.

