# 14) Retell integration changes

## Existing likely flow

Retell agent -> webhook -> callout handler -> coverage engine

## New flow

Retell agent -> action orchestration API -> planner/resolver/permissions -> canonical executor -> domain services

## Required Retell-facing endpoints

* /ai-actions/voice
* /ai-actions/sms
* /ai-actions/confirm
* /ai-actions/clarify

## Security requirement

Retell webhook requests must be signature-verified before action execution. Existing Retell docs support request verification using the signature header. This is mandatory now that more destructive actions are allowed over the phone/SMS surface.

