# 23) Final recommendation

Backfill should adopt an **AI-native, shared-action architecture**.

That means:

* keep Retell on phone and SMS,
* build your own native web AI prompt layer,
* use one common action orchestration system underneath,
* and enforce channel-specific guardrails so each surface only does what it handles well.

This is the cleanest way to evolve the existing Backfill Shifts product without throwing away the work already defined in the original engineering package.

It preserves the structured UI,
adds a powerful AI control layer,
and turns the phone number into a real operational remote control without making it the entire admin product.
